            <title>[FLINK-22577] KubernetesLeaderElectionAndRetrievalITCase is failing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-22577</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;KubernetesLeaderElectionAndRetrievalITCase&lt;/tt&gt; is failing constantly. Running it locally results in an &lt;tt&gt;AssertionError&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
